# solstice and equinox are starts of astrological seasons

# wheel of the year
# -----------------
* nov  1, samhain,  winter start
* dec 21, yule,     winter solstice
# jan 31, imbolc,   winter end

* feb  1, imbolc,   spring start
* mar 20, ostara,   spring equinox
# apr 30, beltane,  spring end

* may  1, beltane,  summer start
* jun 21, litha,    summer solstice
# jul 31, lughnasa, summer end

* aug  1, lughnasa, fall start
* sep 23, mabon,    fall equinox
# oct 31, samhain,  fall end

