m=feb & w=mon & a=3,    Presidents' Day
m=may & w=mon & b=1,    Memorial Day
* jun 19,             Juneteenth: Black Independence Day
m=jul & c=4,           Independence Day (holiday)
m=sep & w=mon & a=1,    Labor Day (US)
m=oct & w=mon & a=2,    Columbus Day
* nov 11,             Veterans Day
m=nov & w=thu & a=4,    Thanksgiving Day (US)

m=jan & w=mon & a=3,Martin Luther King, Jr. Day
